               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Täʾamrä Maryam "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 2ra-28va)&#xD;
I-1) Mäṣḥafä śǝrʿat, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 2ra-5rb)&#xD;
I-2) Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 5rb-8rb)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsäggǝd läki wä-ʾǝweddǝsäki ... "I worship Thee ..." (fol. 8va-9va)&#xD;
I-4) Täʾamrä Maryam "Miracles of Mary": 20 miracles (fols. 9va-28va)&#xD;
II) Excerpt from a lectionary (fols. 29ra-36vb)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-2 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Māryām ʾǝmmu lä-ʾIyasus Krǝstos kähali ... "O my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of Jesus Christ the Almighty ..." (fol. 7rb-va) (cp. ChRep no. 373)</note>
                     <note>- salām laki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Māryām ʾǝmmä mädḫǝn wä-ʾǝmmä bǝrhan ... "Salutation to you, o my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of the Saviour and Mother of the Light ..."(fols. 7va-8rb).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The miracles of Text I-4 are not numbered.</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>The arrangement of Text II is similar to the scriptural readings for the days of the week, cp. Ms. S<ref type="mss" corresp="ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>(Mäṣḥafä gǝṣṣǝw) for</note>
                     <note>- Sunday: fols. 29ra-31vb (S<ref type="mss" corresp="ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>: fols. 54vb-59ra)</note>
                     <note>- Friday: fols. 31vb-34rb (S<ref type="mss" corresp="ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>: fols. 50rb-52ra)</note>
                     <note>- Saturday: fols. 34rb-36vb (S<ref type="mss" corresp="ESdgm007">DGM-007</ref>: fols. 52ra-54vb).</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
